						               													<description>Oh no! A magical tornado has devastated the library and torn away the pages of the grimoire. Apprentice magicians, it's up to you to make up stories and bring back the pages... in the correct order!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Team Story, players are either Listener or Storytellers. Once 20 cards are placed face down and the scroll board is created, each Storytellers pick 3 cards without letting the  Listener see them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Storyteller starts and continue the story using a card from their hand. Once they take part in the story with a card, they place it on the scroll board face down and draw another one from the pool. When the scroll board is full, the round ends. All cards are shuffled and given to the Listener. They now have to retrace the story.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But wait! Some cards have Twins! Will you be able to find the correct card and remake the story through the cards in 60 seconds?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends once everyone has been Listener once. The player who scored the most stars wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
